### Pricing Service API Tests

### 1. Calculate Price - New Car (2023)
POST http://localhost:8086/api/v1/pricing/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": 1,
  "brand": "Maruti Suzuki",
  "model": "Swift",
  "year": 2023,
  "odometer": 5000,
  "originalPrice": 800000
}

